A basic power manager daemon.
Picture of Zelos from
http://media.giantbomb.com/uploads/0/3614/186239-zelos_wilder.._large.jpg.

Requires:
pm-utils
xcowsay
acpi
zsh

To install or update:
sudo ./aionis-setup

To make sure aionis is run at startup, add it to the daemons array in
/etc/rc.conf:
DAEMONS=(... aionis)
